<article id="post-44723" class="post-44723 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-events-and-life category-mindsets category-sports category-wellbeing tag-exercise tag-kids tag-park tag-play-time tag-running entry kind-">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/04/02/todays-alternative-to-my-usual-run/" rel="bookmark">Today&#8217;s alternative to my usual run</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
		<figure class="post-thumbnail">
			<a class="post-thumbnail-inner" href="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/04/02/todays-alternative-to-my-usual-run/" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
				<img width="1568" height="1176" src="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?fit=1568%2C1176&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image" alt="" data-attachment-id="44725" data-permalink="https://pauljacobson.me/20190402_181101-01/" data-orig-file="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?fit=4608%2C3456&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="4608,3456" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;1.9&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;SM-A720F&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1554228661&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;3.6&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;40&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0028409090909091&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="20190402_181101-01.jpeg" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?fit=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?fit=640%2C480&amp;ssl=1" data-lazy-srcset="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?w=4608&amp;ssl=1 4608w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?resize=700%2C525&amp;ssl=1 700w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?resize=1568%2C1176&amp;ssl=1 1568w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" data-lazy-src="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_181101-01.jpeg?fit=1568%2C1176&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" />			</a>
		</figure>

			
	<div class="entry-content">
		
<div class="wp-block-image wp-image-44724 size-medium"><figure class="alignright is-resized"><img src="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_182132-013769549471483119203.jpeg?resize=258%2C287&#038;ssl=1" alt="Frisbee and a ball" width="258" height="287" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_182132-013769549471483119203.jpeg?resize=258%2C287&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" class=" jetpack-lazy-image"><noscript><img src="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/20190402_182132-013769549471483119203.jpeg?resize=258%2C287&#038;ssl=1" alt="Frisbee and a ball" width="258" height="287" data-recalc-dims="1" /></noscript><figcaption>Our frisbee and ball</figcaption></figure></div>



<p>I finally took some time to get outside, and exercise for the first time in about a week. I was going to do my usual run (it&#8217;s effective but I don&#8217;t particularly like it) when my daughter asked me to take her to the park.</p>



<p>I was about to say &#8220;No&#8221;, and that I wouldn&#8217;t have time, and then it occurred to both of us that I could take her to the park, <em>and</em> get my cardio workout.</p>



<p>So we took a ball and a frisbee. Our daughter (and, later, her friend too), threw the frisbee, or kicked the ball, and I ran around fetching it for them.</p>



<p>This worked out to be a win-win, I think.</p>
