		<figure class="post-thumbnail">
			<a class="post-thumbnail-inner" href="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/03/20/going-to-bed-early-in-theory/" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
				<img width="1568" height="1039" src="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?fit=1568%2C1039&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image" alt="" data-attachment-id="44351" data-permalink="https://pauljacobson.me/pexels-photo-271897/" data-orig-file="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?fit=1880%2C1246&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1880,1246" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="alone bed bedroom blur" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?fit=300%2C199&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?fit=640%2C424&amp;ssl=1" data-lazy-srcset="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?w=1880&amp;ssl=1 1880w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?resize=300%2C199&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?resize=768%2C509&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?resize=700%2C464&amp;ssl=1 700w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?resize=1568%2C1039&amp;ssl=1 1568w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" data-lazy-src="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/pexels-photo-271897.jpeg?fit=1568%2C1039&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" />			</a>
		</figure>

			
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>My wife: I&#8217;m going to bed early, I&#8217;m exhausted.</p>
<p>Me: Good idea! I&#8217;m just going to have my tea (decaf), watch some quick, random video on YouTube, then I&#8217;ll also head to bed early.</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>I finally get to bed about an hour later, after watching about half a dozen videos about having ADHD.</p>
