<article id="post-44070" class="post-44070 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-film tag-movie tag-spider-man tag-spider-verse entry kind-">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/03/16/spider-man-into-the-spider-verse-is-one-of-the-best-movies-ive-seen/" rel="bookmark">Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse is one of the best movies I&#8217;ve seen</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
		<figure class="post-thumbnail">
			<a class="post-thumbnail-inner" href="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/03/16/spider-man-into-the-spider-verse-is-one-of-the-best-movies-ive-seen/" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
				<img width="1568" height="882" src="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?fit=1568%2C882&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image" alt="Spider-Man poster" data-attachment-id="44071" data-permalink="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/03/16/spider-man-into-the-spider-verse-is-one-of-the-best-movies-ive-seen/spider-man_miles_morales_minimalist_poster_descktop/" data-orig-file="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?fit=1920%2C1080&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1920,1080" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop" data-image-description="&lt;p&gt;Spider-Man poster by Abijithka, licensed CC BY SA 4.0&lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?fit=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?fit=640%2C360&amp;ssl=1" data-lazy-srcset="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?resize=700%2C394&amp;ssl=1 700w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?resize=1568%2C882&amp;ssl=1 1568w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" data-lazy-src="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png?fit=1568%2C882&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" />			</a>
		</figure>

			
	<div class="entry-content">
		
<p class="has-drop-cap">We finally watched <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4633694/?ref_=nv_sr_1" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse (opens in a new tab)">Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse</a>, and it&#8217;s comfortably one of the best movies I&#8217;ve seen.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed-youtube alignwide wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<span class="embed-youtube" style="text-align:center; display: block;"><iframe class='youtube-player' type='text/html' width='640' height='360' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/FU0i0eg6qak?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent' allowfullscreen='true' style='border:0;'></iframe></span>
</div></figure>



<p>The story is compelling, the animation is brilliantly done. It&#8217;s just <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="an incredible movie (opens in a new tab)" href="http://www.intothespiderverse.movie/" target="_blank">an incredible movie</a>. If you haven&#8217;t seen it, and you&#8217;re curious, it&#8217;s well worth watching.</p>



<p>This movie was the first of two movies we have planned for today. This afternoon, we&#8217;re going to watch <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="Aquaman (opens in a new tab)" href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1477834/?ref_=nv_sr_1" target="_blank">Aquaman</a>. DC movies tend not to be as good as Marvel movies, so I&#8217;m holding thumbs that Aquaman lives up to the hype. <strong><em>Update:</em></strong><em> I enjoyed Aquaman, but Spider-Man still won the day for me.</em></p>



<p class="has-small-font-size">Featured image: <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="Spider-Man Miles Morales Minimalist Poster descktop (opens in a new tab)" href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Spider-Man_Miles_Morales_Minimalist_Poster_descktop.png" target="_blank">Spider-Man Miles Morales Minimalist Poster descktop</a> by <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="Abijithka (opens in a new tab)" href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Abijithka" target="_blank">Abijithka</a>, licensed <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="CC BY SA 4.0 International (opens in a new tab)" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/deed.en" target="_blank">CC BY SA 4.0 International</a></p>



<p><strong>Postscript:</strong> Not only was the movie really good, but I love the soundtrack. Actually, there are two soundtracks: <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="Daniel Pemberton's instrumental soundtrack (opens in a new tab)" href="https://open.spotify.com/album/5KP2NReDL2Bv0QLzHSvUwM?si=6gRV7F8_ST6PHPmG6XrDfA" target="_blank">Daniel Pemberton&#8217;s instrumental soundtrack</a>, and <a href="https://open.spotify.com/album/35s58BRTGAEWztPo9WqCIs?si=IVbwDFJBQJmH3UuJM9j82A" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="the music from (and inspired by) the movie (opens in a new tab)">the music from (and inspired by) the movie</a>. Of the two, I definitely prefer the instrumental soundtrack, and I suspect it will be on heavy rotation in the coming days:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed-spotify aligncenter wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-spotify wp-embed-aspect-9-16 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe width="300" height="380" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" allow="encrypted-media" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/5KP2NReDL2Bv0QLzHSvUwM"></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p>This one track from the other soundtrack, &#8220;<a href="https://open.spotify.com/track/5zsHmE2gO3RefVsPyw2e3T?si=mGg7fU3HRyaShy3c-u55lg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="What's Up Danger (opens in a new tab)">What&#8217;s Up Danger</a>&#8221; really appeals to me too!</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed-spotify aligncenter wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-spotify wp-embed-aspect-9-16 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe width="300" height="380" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" allow="encrypted-media" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/5zsHmE2gO3RefVsPyw2e3T"></iframe>
</div></figure>
