<article id="post-43881" class="post-43881 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-events-and-life category-webtech tag-web30 entry kind-">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/03/13/happy-30th-birthday-to-the-web/" rel="bookmark">Happy 30th birthday to the Web</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
		<figure class="post-thumbnail">
			<a class="post-thumbnail-inner" href="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/03/13/happy-30th-birthday-to-the-web/" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
				<img width="1568" height="1176" src="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?fit=1568%2C1176&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image" alt="Cake for the Web @ 30" data-attachment-id="43883" data-permalink="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/03/13/happy-30th-birthday-to-the-web/cake-web30-smaller/" data-orig-file="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?fit=2000%2C1500&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="2000,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;iPhone SE&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1552385594&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;4.15&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;125&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.03030303030303&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="Cake-web@30-smaller" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?fit=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?fit=640%2C480&amp;ssl=1" data-lazy-srcset="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?w=2000&amp;ssl=1 2000w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?resize=700%2C525&amp;ssl=1 700w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?resize=1568%2C1176&amp;ssl=1 1568w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w, https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" data-lazy-src="https://i2.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Cake-web@30-smaller.jpg?fit=1568%2C1176&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" />			</a>
		</figure>

			
	<div class="entry-content">
		
<p>The Web turned 30 yesterday, so I guess this is a belated birthday post about the invention that made so much of how I live my life, and my various careers, possible.</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>In 1989 the worldâs largest physics laboratory, CERN, was a hive of  ideas and information stored on multiple incompatible computers. Sir Tim  Berners-Lee envisioned a unifying structure for linking information  across different computers, and wrote a proposal in March 1989 called &#8220;<a href="https://cds.cern.ch/record/369245/files/dd-89-001.pdf">InformationÂ Management: A Proposal</a>&#8220;.Â By 1991 this vision of universal connectivity had become the World Wide Web.</p><cite><a href="https://web30.web.cern.ch/">30th Anniversary of the World Wide Web | Web at 30: Celebrating the 30th Anniversary of the Invention of the Web</a></cite></blockquote>



<p>I love that the comment on Tim Berners-Lee&#8217;s <a href="https://cds.cern.ch/record/369245/files/dd-89-001.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="original proposal (opens in a new tab)">original proposal</a> for the Web was &#8220;<a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="Vague, but exciting (opens in a new tab)" href="http://info.cern.ch/Proposal.html" target="_blank">Vague, but exciting</a>&#8221; &#x1f602;.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><img src="https://i2.wp.com/info.cern.ch/images/proposal.gif?w=640" alt data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i2.wp.com/info.cern.ch/images/proposal.gif?w=640&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" class=" jetpack-lazy-image"><noscript><img src="https://i2.wp.com/info.cern.ch/images/proposal.gif?w=640" alt="" data-recalc-dims="1"/></noscript></figure></div>



<p>The CERN team put together <a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/6LdKg7uXYsDBPnsiQvHZda" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="a Spotify playlist (opens in a new tab)">a Spotify playlist</a> including music from when the Web was created. If you were alive back then, this may bring back memories:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed-spotify aligncenter wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-spotify wp-embed-aspect-9-16 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe width="300" height="380" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" allow="encrypted-media" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/6LdKg7uXYsDBPnsiQvHZda"></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p>It&#8217;s also pretty interesting to read what people have to say about this anniversary of the Web. Take a look at this Twitter stream based on the <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="#Web30 hashtag (opens in a new tab)" href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Web30" target="_blank">#Web30 hashtag</a>.</p>



<p class="has-small-font-size">Image credit: <a href="https://cds.cern.ch/record/2665683" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="CERN (opens in a new tab)">CERN</a> (I didn&#8217;t see a specific license, so hopefully it&#8217;s an open license)</p>
