<article id="post-43769" class="post-43769 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-music category-wellbeing tag-anxiety tag-depression tag-music-2 tag-vance-joy entry kind-">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/03/11/feeling-a-bit-better-with-this-song/" rel="bookmark">Feeling a bit better with this song</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
		<figure class="post-thumbnail">
			<a class="post-thumbnail-inner" href="https://pauljacobson.me/2019/03/11/feeling-a-bit-better-with-this-song/" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
				<img width="740" height="430" src="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hike_up_Givat_HaTitora-18-2000.jpg?fit=740%2C430&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image" alt="" data-attachment-id="41774" data-permalink="https://pauljacobson.me/hike_up_givat_hatitora-18-2000/" data-orig-file="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hike_up_Givat_HaTitora-18-2000.jpg?fit=2000%2C1324&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="2000,1324" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D5100&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1544888671&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;50&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0003125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Hike_up_Givat_HaTitora-18-2000" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hike_up_Givat_HaTitora-18-2000.jpg?fit=300%2C199&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hike_up_Givat_HaTitora-18-2000.jpg?fit=640%2C423&amp;ssl=1" data-lazy-srcset="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hike_up_Givat_HaTitora-18-2000.jpg?resize=740%2C430&amp;ssl=1 740w, https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hike_up_Givat_HaTitora-18-2000.jpg?zoom=2&amp;resize=740%2C430&amp;ssl=1 1480w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" data-lazy-src="https://i1.wp.com/pauljacobson.me/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hike_up_Givat_HaTitora-18-2000.jpg?fit=740%2C430&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" />			</a>
		</figure>

			
	<div class="entry-content">
		
<p>I&#8217;ve had a rough week or two with more anxiety and depression than usual. Music tends to help my mood, and &#8220;<a href="https://open.spotify.com/track/3P4spaSr7co8diWOj72X9A?si=j5FElvM2S3a9F3L-upAOcw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="Like Gold (opens in a new tab)">Like Gold</a>&#8221; by Vance Joy is one of those songs for me:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed-spotify alignwide wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-spotify wp-embed-aspect-9-16 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/3P4spaSr7co8diWOj72X9A%3Fsi%3Dj5FElvM2S3a9F3L-upAOcw" width="300" height="380" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" allow="encrypted-media"></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p>Actually, I&#8217;m really enjoying Vance Joy generally at the moment. Here&#8217;a a great playlist to binge with:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed-spotify alignwide wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-spotify wp-embed-aspect-9-16 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
